title: Death Note Manga Collection(w/ B.B.)
description:
Death Note Manga Collection(w/ B.B.)

This collection is a Rar file that you must extract.
Download WinRar if you need a program to extract the files.

The Rar Consists of:


-Volumes 1-12 (Main story)
-Volume 13    (How to read)
-Chapter 109  (Special)
-Pilot        (Death Erasor)
-Fake Ending
-Death Note Another Note The Los Angeles BB Murder Cases (.PDF BOOK)



This is just a collection of all the Death Note Manga i could find.



ENJOY AND SEED!
